high_descs: Turn around to your right and head to the right side of the stove
Pick up the spoon on the counter in front of the salt
Turn around to your left and head to the sink
Put the spoon on the sink, rinse it and pick up the spoon
Turn to your right and face the  stove
Pull the cabinet drawer beside the stove and put inside the spoon then close the drawer
anns.task_desc: Put the clean spoon on the cabinet drawer.

high_descs: Turn around and walk straight then turn left and face the counter to the right of the stove
Pick up the metal spoon from the counter
Turn to the left and walk to the kitchen sink and face it
Place the spoon in the sink and rinse it off with water then pick it back up
Turn to the right and face the counter to the left of the stove
Open the drawer on your left in the corner and place the clean spoon inside
anns.task_desc: Wash a metal spoon and put it away in the drawer

high_descs: Move to the counter to the right of the sink
Pick up a spoon from the counter
Move to the sink to the left of you
Clean the spoon in the sink
Move to the counter to the left of the stove
Put the spoon in the drawer to the right of sink
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned spoon in the drawer to the right of sink.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the counter turn right and walk to the counter to the right of the stove
Pick up the spoon that is sitting on the counter
Turn left and head to the sink
Place the spoon into the sink on top of the knife. Turn on the faucet then turn off the faucet
Pick up the spoon
Turn right and open the drawer that is to the right of the sink. Place the spoon in the drawer then close the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean spoon in a drawer.

high_descs: Turn around and walk toward the counter, then turn left and walk to the oven.
Pick up the spoon that is on the counter next to the stovetop.
Turn around and step forward, then turn right and walk to the sink.
Wash the spoon in the sink.
Pick up the spoon out of the sink.
Turn right and open the drawer by the sink and place the spoon inside, then close the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean spoon into a drawer.

high_descs: turn to the right twice and go to the counter top and turn to the left and go to the counter top
pick up the spoon from the counter top
turn to the left twice take a few steps and turn to the right and go to the front of the sink
put the spoon in the sink and turn on the water to fill it up and turn off and drain the water and pick up the spoon up from the sink
turn to the right
open the drawer and put the spoon in it and close the drawer
anns.task_desc: Place a washed spoon in a drawer.
